{"tid":1832264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇返澳門政府啲舉動 隻肺炎應該呢兩日突然變得好大鑊","createTime":"2020-01-21T04:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T06:26:06.000Z","uid":20241,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e5254ddd2a3420c3e728192cfb331d21b70001","tid":1832264,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"今日澳門政府記者會直播話會成立個應變小組<br />\n聽日所有支那航班要測體溫<br />\n應該收到風出大事"},{"pid":"0c9ecbccf12d3f542d2a09ac020f22934c76a2c3","tid":1832264,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">一日到黑就淨係錢, 樓價股價, 69已經話緊人收錢出黎行</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#20241 - 高息股</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>我有一計可破黃色經濟圈 在此獻上希望可以俾個AO小妹做下 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>最近班黑衣暴徒越來越倡狂<br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n只要分出邊啲係黃店<br />\n再安排防暴長駐 入店既年青人全部都要查證+事後拘捕(擾亂社會秩序+非法集結)<br />\n咁樣黃色經濟圈好快就會不攻自破<br />\n香港好快可以回復正常<br />\n希望特首接納</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1802010/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1802010/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>冇事啦香港人贏左啦港女升返曬啦大家快啲返工返學啦 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>各位手足付出左咁多<br />\n贏得咁辛苦<br />\n大家俾啲掌聲自己好唔好<br />\n好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Flomoji%2F12.png&h=b2e0eb94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Flm2%2Fsupport.gif&h=4d4183e9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1758161/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1758161/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>水炮車其實都幾大部 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>支持警察係大街射死你地班暴徒<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1664677/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1664677/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>核彈都唔割！嗱不過搞裝修 紅綠燈 叫太多神獸就割架啦 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>始終人種同基因係咁就係咁<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1628233/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1628233/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港太亂 希望政府強力執法 全港斷網 斷電話3日搜捕暴徒 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>周圍破壞 又上網亂咁抹黑警方同政府<br />\n我地一般市民真係忍唔到啦！<br />\n應立即斷網斷電話 實施戒嚴三日 趁呢段時間啲甲由冇得走一網打盡<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1618273/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1618273/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kBN5bas.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"e4bc4569764d56bad5cff6a291f012885e958216","tid":1832264,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒"},{"pid":"19fff3844e2bd40abb4bab3492a1065a18a0d5de","tid":1832264,"uid":34816,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"連澳門咁撚廢都即刻推防疫措施，港共wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都好，快d攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10455a0fa28fd6f6f2a1725bdaed950e2accc835","tid":1832264,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"失晒控<br />\n可能變風土病"},{"pid":"8a6c7927d7c6a305da196a300c6224055f83b406","tid":1832264,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19fff3844e2bd40abb4bab3492a1065a18a0d5de","tid":1832264,"uid":34816,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"連澳門咁撚廢都即刻推防疫措施，港共wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都好，快d攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"沃豬要錢<br />\n港共要奶<br />\n目的唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e8d063c71756d053d4ca681f2ee0e6467ed207","tid":1832264,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n党愛世人，愛你，沒事兒！"},{"pid":"8063